item.title: Why you should practice writing
item.description: Lately, I have been obsessed with Janelle Monáe. This obsession began with her latest album “Dirty Computer”. I admire how articulate and thoughtful she is with everything that she does. So I did what any true fan would do: I tried to watch as many interviews with Janelle Monáe as possible.

item.title: About
item.description: My name is Khanh Nghiem (b. 1997). I was born in Hanoi, Vietnam and moved to the US for college in 2015. I am currently living in Austin, TX. My day job is at Google Cloud, in a one-year talent development program where I received intensive training on cloud technology and business skills before rotating through different positions across the company.
